commit.message:
render-assets.py: Drop oxipng --libdeflater flag

Libdeflater is enabled by default in oxipng 7.0.0, and the script
would fail when the --libdeflater flag was included in the command.
The script still works with older oxipng versions, but libdeflater
is not used, so the optimized assets would be sligtly larger.

verification.payload:
tree cee2f9930264f5f9b011c0f6f7ab770a832e632a
parent 3fd4786f45ce18f06eb8c2efeee6510bb45fabe8
author Joonas Henriksson <joonas.henriksson@gmail.com> 1671390004 +0200
committer Joonas Henriksson <joonas.henriksson@gmail.com> 1671390288 +0200

render-assets.py: Drop oxipng --libdeflater flag

Libdeflater is enabled by default in oxipng 7.0.0, and the script
would fail when the --libdeflater flag was included in the command.
The script still works with older oxipng versions, but libdeflater
is not used, so the optimized assets would be sligtly larger.
